text.tspan: Israel: New hospitalizations for severe COVID-19 by age
Shown is the rolling weekly sum of severe hospitalizations. Data is available at the national level, plus breakdown
by regions where vaccination began early or late.
Vaccination in Israel began on December 19 2020. Israel imposed a third national lockdown on January 8 2021.
